snippet.title: HERO'S ODYSSEY - Anime Isekai Visual Novel - Trailer
snippet.description:
🕹 Play Demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3309270?utm_campaign=youtube

Check out the "Hero's Odyssey Demo" trailer for this adventurous visual novel.

As an ordinary guy, you get teleported to Ancient Greece, where Zeus himself gives you a thrilling mission!

Meet extraordinary friends and romance mythological characters! 
Try not to break their hearts ~
